OL,6,FRealising what was happening, he held
OL,7,Fonto the passenger door as Ross sped
OL,8,Foff.
OL,10,FProsecutor John Harrison KC told the
OL,11,Fcourt: "Unfortunately his actions did
OL,12,Fnot prevent the defendant from driving
OL,13,Faway, with Mr Kondor hanging on to his
OL,14,Fvan."
OL,16,FCCTV footage played in court showed Mr
OL,17,FKondor hanging onto the moving van
OL,18,Fthrough an open door as Ross drove
OL,19,Faway along Wingate Road.
