OL,6,FHis feet were dragged along the road
OL,7,Fas Ross swerved the van around at
OL,8,Fspeed. The court heard witnesses heard
OL,9,FMr Kondor shouting for help, fearing
OL,10,Ffor his life.
OL,12,F"It appears Mr Kondor did not wish to
OL,13,For perhaps could not let go of his
OL,14,Fvan, he did not want the defendant
OL,15,Fsimply to steal it," Mr Harrison said.
