OL,6,FThe van initially clipped a parked car
OL,7,Fbefore colliding heavily with another
OL,8,Fparked car in Heights Drive, Farnley,
OL,9,Fcausing Mr Kondor catastrophic head
OL,10,Fand chest injuries. He died at the
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,FRoss sped away and arranged for the
OL,14,Fvan to be taken to a back street at
OL,15,FBroom Nook, Belle Isle, to be stripped
OL,16,Fof its parcels.
OL,18,FThe vehicle was then abandoned in
OL,19,FHighlands Walk, Belle Isle, where it
OL,20,Fwas recovered by officers after its on-
OL,21,Fboard tracker was followed.
