OL,6,FRoss claimed he was unaware of Mr
OL,7,FKondor hanging onto the van and said
OL,8,Fhe had crashed into the parked car
OL,9,Fafter losing control on speed bumps.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said Ross had collided
OL,12,Fwith the car deliberately to knock him
OL,13,Foff.
OL,15,F"Claudiu was a decent hard-working man
OL,16,Fand it's clear he was determined not
OL,17,Fto let Ross take his livelihood. For
OL,18,Fhalf a mile he bravely clung to the
OL,19,Fopen door as Ross swerved the van
OL,20,Faround at speed before deliberately
OL,21,Fcrashing leaving him fatally injured.
