OL,6,F"Claudiu came to the UK from Romania
OL,7,Fto make a better life for himself. He
OL,8,Fwas described by his work colleagues
OL,9,Fas being not just a dedicated and
OL,10,Fvalued member of their team but a
OL,11,Ffriend and a confidant. He was also a
OL,12,Ffamiliar friendly face to the many
OL,13,Fpeople he delivered to."
OL,15,F"His partner, who had also come to the
OL,16,FUK for work, has since returned to
OL,17,FRomania now seeing no future here. She
OL,18,Fand Claudiu's family have been left
OL,19,Futterly devastated by his death.
