OL,6,F"Through the hard work, dedication and
OL,7,Fcommitment of everyone involved, from
OL,8,Fthose initial attending officers, the
OL,9,Fpublic providing information and CCTV,
OL,10,Fto the analytical and support staff
OL,11,Fand the detectives there throughout
OL,12,Fthe investigation to its conclusion at
OL,13,Fcourt, we have been able to provide
OL,14,Fjustice for Claudiu and his family."
